text:
Police are warning of delays after a lorry's blown over on the A1 in Cambridgeshire. It happened at Brampton Hut.
The driver escaped from his crumpled cab with minor head injuries.
A lorry was blown over on the A1 at Brampton Hut in Cambridgeshire. Credit: Matthew Hudson / ITV News Anglia Cambs police @CambsCops Follow #RTC #Brampton Hut #A14 Lorry blown over expect delays
